<plot>Professor Owl is lecturing to his class of bird and animal students, when they students interrupt him with weather questions regarding what makes the north wind blow and what makes snow. As the good professor starts to explain this phenomenon, the scene shits to the North Pole where little dwarfs are shown in the process of making snow, thunder and wind.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?503580</url></doc>
